  "keyFeatures": [
    "Second-order accurate AMR staggered-grid solver for two-phase flows",
    "Support for Newtonian and non-Newtonian (viscoelastic Oldroyd-B) fluid models",
    "Efficient multigrid FAC preconditioner for saddle-point systems",
    "Gradient-based adaptive mesh refinement for resolving sharp interfaces",
    "Multiple convective operator limiter types: UPWIND, CUI, FBICS, MGAMMA",
    "CFL-stable time stepping with trapezoidal rule and Adams-Bashforth schemes",
    "Built on IBAMR/SAMRAI/PETSc for scalable parallel computation",
    "VisIt-compatible visualization output"
  ],
